The Sage - Powers and Rules

Flight
	Buff
	Reduce Attack damage taken by 50%. Cancelled if dealt Attack damage X times in one turn. Otherwise, the value is reset at the start of your turn to the value at the end of your last turn.
Air
	Air effects only have an effect if you have at least 1 Flight.
Brew
	You obtain a Potion in X turns, either now (X=0) or at the start of that turn. If you don't have  empty potion slots at that point, you must use it immediately or discard it.
		-> Hier musst du sagen, wie sich das implementieren lässt, kannst evtl. die Regel auch so abändern, dass man ohne Slots einfach keinen Trank bekommt.
Brewing
	Buff: 
	You brew potions X turns faster.
Disoriented
	Debuff:
	If you fly, the enemy attacks you one time less, for X turns.
		-> Einfache Angriffe werden dadurch komplett auf 0 gesetzt (Hyperbeam!)

Gaining Artifacts is not considered a debuff.